= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) - Enemies =

This page documents the enemy data structure in Dragon Warrior IV.

'''Data Status:''' Monster data structure verified from Bank 6/7. Enemy type table at Bank 19 $b967.

== Overview ==

Each monster in Dragon Warrior IV is defined by approximately 27 bytes of data. The monster tables are stored in Banks 6-8, with additional type data in Bank 19.

