== Metal Flags (Byte 22, +$16) ==

Controls special monster types, particularly Metal monsters.

{| class="wikitable"
! Bits !! Mask !! Description
|-
| 0-1 || $03 || Metal flag ($11 = Metal monster, immune to most damage)
|-
| 2-7 || $fc || Unknown (usually zero)
|}

